# components

**Instance Property**

A dictionary containing the components of a type checking result.

## Declaration

```swift
var components: [NSTextCheckingKey : String]? { get }
```

## Discussion

Currently used by the transit checking result. The supported keys are located in [doc://com.apple.foundation/documentation/Foundation/keys-for-transit-components].

## Related Documentation

- **transitInformationCheckingResult(range:components:)**: Creates and returns a text checking result with the specified transit information.
